column5: anyone up for it? with weather permitting, i'd love to get out try for some.. but.. to let you know.. i'm a total beginner on using my baitcaster and rarely fish downtown besides the spits.. but i'm sure there are plenty of you that can help me out.. right?? well reply back here and i'm sure we'd have  atleast a few of us going..
Make it the weekend and I'd love to join you and anyone else but can't pull of tomorrow, damn job always getting in the way
im in for it tommorow, between 12 and 4 or so...
I'm in, drop me a p.m to where you wanna meet i am avail from 10am till 3 p.m..
